data.description: Lots of elbow room inside and outside of this manufactured home. Spacious 2 bedroom, 2 bath floor plan with separate living room room and family room. Remodeled kitchen with custom cabinets and updated appliances. Utility room with laundry hook-ups and lots of storage/pantry area. Economical kerosene monitor heater; both evaporative cooling and window AC. Large detached metal carport, storage sheds and garden area, all on oversize 1/2 acre lot.
